st%20pork%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Ong%2C%20a%2049-year-old%20officer%20with%20the%20Singapore%20Armed%20Forces%2C%20said%20he%20found%20Leong's%20stall%20last%20year%20and%20has%20been%20having%20it%20about%20thrice%20a%20week%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOng%20said%20the%20sides%20are%20just%20as%20good.%20The%20flavorful%20rice%20and%20jammy%20eggs%2C%20which%20deviate%20from%20the%20usual%20hard-boiled%20eggs%20served%20with%20char%20siu%2C%20add%20to%20its%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20regulars%20who%20rave%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20numerous%20food%20bloggers%20in%20Singapore%20have%20reported%20on%20Leong's%20stall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESethlui.com%2C%20a%20prominent%20local%20food%20publication%2C%20said%20in%20a%20July%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsethlui.com%2Fchar-siu-lang-singapore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Char%20Siu%20Lang%20that%20the%20pork%20was%20%26quot%3Bcaramelized%20to%20perfection%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20compete%20with%20bigger%20Chinese%20food%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Singapore%2C%20small%20stalls%20like%20Leong's%20are%20known%20to%20serve%20world-class%20fare%2C%20including%20some%20that%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-cheapest-michelin-starred-meal-singapore-noodles-review-photos-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Michelin%20Guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210ef0bf0-8371-4b1e-8cc0-00a98e44fd64%5C%22%3EBut%20for%20Leong%2C%20the%20endgame%20looks%20like%20getting%20out%20of%20the%20kitchen%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Leong%2C%20trading%20corporate%20life%20for%20days%20sweating%20in%20front%20of%20a%20charcoal%20oven%20was%20tough%2C%20with%20everything%20from%20time%20management%20to%20his%20physical%20appearance%20having%20to%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLifestyle-wise%2C%20when%20I%20was%20doing%20financial%20advisory%2C%20I%20dressed%20up%2C%20used%20perfume%2C%20and%20wore%20all%20the%20brands.%20But%20in%20the%20shop%2C%20I%20just%20wear%20whatever%20is%20comfortable%2C%20maybe%20a%20pair%20of%20shorts%2C%20my%20company%20T-shirt%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20wear%20safety%20boots%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20insurance%20job%20also%20allowed%20for%20more%20flexibility%2C%20where%20he%20could%20just%20%26quot%3Bpush%20the%20appointment%2C%20change%20the%20timings%26quot%3B%20for%20client%20meetings.%20But%20reaching%20his%20stall%20at%207%20a.m.%20daily%20is%20a%20schedule%20that%20requires%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20business%2C%20Leong%20immediately%20answered%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20endgame%20is%20to%20sell%20the%20business%20to%20big%20organizations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20long%20work%20hours%20are%20not%20something%20he%20thinks%20he%20can%20sustain%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20return%20to%20a%20corporate%20job%20is%20off%20the%20table%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20wants%20to%20sell%20something%20of%20his%20own%2C%20explore%20new%20business%20ventures%2C%20and%20not%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20love%20to%20know%2C%20be%20able%20to%20do%20other%20things%2C%20not%20only%20spend%20my%20time%20in%20the%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20Leong%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20times%20to%20come%2C%20I%20really%20need%20to%20take%20a%20step%20back%20because%20I%20really%20feel%20like%20I%20spend%20too%20much%20time%20in%20this%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhe-won-lottery-quit-insurance-job-opened-roast-pork-stall-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744935482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c9670bb1834fe311665102%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhe-won-lotte