nology%20at%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapero%20shared%20three%20ways%20he%20has%20been%20using%20AI%20to%20become%20more%20efficient%20in%20his%20day-to-day%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20aspects%20of%20his%20job%20he%20still%20prefers%20to%20do%20manually%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ac158ed-f0d7-46e3-8ce4-d6d1f42d1b0c%5C%22%3E1.%20You%20can't%20be%20everywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20Shapero%20said%20he%20uses%20AI%20is%20to%20summarize%20notes%20for%20meetings%20he%20misses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20meetings%20that%20I%20think%20would've%20been%20valuable%20to%20attend%2C%20but%20sometimes%20I%20can't%20be%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShapero%20said%20he%20likes%20using%20Copilot%20for%20this%20because%20it%20is%20built%20into%20Teams%2C%20which%20the%20Microsoft-owned%20company%20uses.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20often%20use%20Copilot%20to%20summarize%20meeting%20outcomes%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20can%20stay%20on%20top%20of%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cc3d0d3-ed87-4136-84ea-0a838926df50%5C%22%3E2.%20Unfamiliar%20topics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShapero%20also%20said%20he%20uses%20AI%20to%20learn%20about%20topics%20he%20is%20not%20well%20versed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOftentimes%2C%20I'll%20have%20to%20learn%20about%20new%20technologies%2C%20new%20legislation%2C%20and%20different%20industry%20trends%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20COO%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20that%20having%20a%20conversation%20with%20ChatGPT%20can%20be%20very%20helpful%20in%20me%20learning%20deeply%20about%20a%20topic%20that%20I'm%20not%20familiar%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3dfe77a-2668-4c03-a222-66ea1900eb3b%5C%22%3E3.%20Preparing%20for%20meetings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShapero%20said%20he%20also%20likes%20using%20AI%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20for%20meeting%20prep.%20He%20said%20he%20uses%20LinkedIn's%20Account%20IQ%20product%2C%20which%20is%20gea