Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20has%20signed%20a%20%2430%20million%20deal%20with%20Palantir%20for%20software%20add-ons%20to%20track%20self-deportations%20and%20immigrants%20who%20have%20overstayed%20their%20visas%2C%20government%20records%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20contract%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20said%20the%20Immigration%20Lifecycle%20Operating%20System%20%E2%80%94%20or%20ImmigrationOS%20%E2%80%94%20will%20minimize%20%26quot%3Btime%20and%20resource%20expenditure%26quot%3B%20for%20selecting%20and%20apprehending%20immigrants%20based%20on%20ICE%20enforcement%20priorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20%26quot%3Bviolent%20criminals%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Baffiliates%20of%20known%20transnational%20criminal%20organizations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20contract%20also%20cited%20visa%20overstays%20as%20a%20deportation%20priority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImmigrationOS%20will%20expand%20ICE's%20case%20management%20system%20to%20include%20%26quot%3Bnear%20real-time%20visibility%20into%20instances%20of%20self-deportation.%26quot%3B%20The%20contract%20said%20the%20new%20ImmigrationOS%20will%20streamline%20%26quot%3Bend%20to%20end%20immigration%20lifecycle%20from%20identification%20to%20removal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20agency%20is%20awarding%20Palantir%20%2429.8%20million%20for%20a%20prototype%20to%20be%20delivered%20by%20September%2025.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20contract%2C%20the%20new%20software%20is%20necessary%20for%20ICE%20to%20carry%20out%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20recent%20executive%20orders%20naming%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20transnational%20organized%20crime%20as%20significant%20national%20security%20threats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20ICE%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20deal%20is%20a%20modification%20to%20an%20existing%20contract.%20Palantir%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20agreement%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20a%20contract%20the%20Biden%20administration%20signed%20with%20the%20defense%20contractor%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palantir.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fhomeland-security-investigations-renews-partnership-with-palantir%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20%26quot%3Boperations%20and%20maintenance%26quot%3B%20support%20services.%20The%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20first%20contracted%20Palantir%20to%20build%20its%20case%20management%20system%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20software%20collates%20information%20from%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20government%20databases%20and%20allows%20DHS%20agents%20to%20keep%20detailed%20records%20on%20potential%20immigration%20violators%20for%20future%20enforcement%20actions.%20It%20includes%20%26quot%3Bdata%20sharing%20with%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20for%20lookout%20and%20seizure%20tracking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20documents%20underscore%20an%20increased%20emphasis%20on%20deporting%20immigrants%20who%20have%20entered%20the%20country%20legally%20but%20may%20have%20violated%20the%20conditions%20of%20their%20visas%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20a%20civil%2C%20not%20a%20criminal%2C%20offense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPalantir%20has%20developed%20deep%20institutional%20knowledge%20of%20ICE%20operations%20over%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20ICE%20wrote%20in%20the%20documents.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20systems%20have%20been%20tailored%20to%20meet%20strict%20DHS%20security%20and%20privacy%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPalantir%20employees%20have%20been%20working%20over%20the%20past%20several%20weeks%20to%20increase%20ICE%20capacity%20to%20track%20immigrants%20already%20given%20a%20final%20order%20of%20remov