n%2FCNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDavid%20Einhorn's%20hedge%20fund%20Greenlight%20Capital%20posted%20an%208.2%25%20return%20in%20the%20first%20quarter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20investors%2C%20Greenlight%20said%20gold%20was%20%26quot%3Bby%20far%20the%20biggest%20winner%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20portfolio.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20firm%20cautioned%20that%20a%20bear%20market%20in%20stocks%20is%20just%20starting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20billionaire%20investor%20struck%20gold%20last%20quarter%20by%2C%20well%2C%20investing%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Einhorn's%20Greenlight%20Capital%20gained%208.2%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20handily%20outpacing%20a%20more-than-4%25%20loss%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20an%20letter%20to%20clients%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20firm%20said%20that%20the%20precious%20metal%20was%20%26quot%3Bby%20far%20the%20biggest%20winner%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20portfolio%2C%20advancing%2019%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGreenlight%2C%20which%20said%20it%20owns%20both%20gold%20bars%20and%20call%20options%2C%20also%20performed%20well%20against%20a%20benchmark%20of%20hedge%20funds.%20The%20average%20fund%20lost%20an%20average%20of%200.4%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20according%20to%20research%20group%20HFR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20said%20inflation%20swaps%20were%20an%20additional%20catalyst%20for%20outperformance.%20Between%20the%20swaps%20and%20gold%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20viewed%20as%20an%20inflation%20hedge%20%E2%80%94%20the%20expectation%20of%20higher%20consumer%20prices%20is%20a%20theme%20across%20the%20Greenlight%20portfolio.%20Forecasts%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-dynamic-pricing-inflation-costs-china-trade-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20inflation%3