Short%20positions%20on%20companies%20that%20%26quot%3Bcater%20to%20liberal%20tastes%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Greenlight%20expects%20that%20Democratic%20consumers%20will%20pull%20back%2C%20given%20their%20disproportionate%20exposure%20to%20recent%20federal%20job%20cuts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20position%20in%20SOFR%20futures%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThese%20investments%20are%20positioned%20to%20profit%20if%20the%20Fed%20cuts%20interest%20rates%20faster%20than%20the%20market%20thinks%2C%20which%20is%20what%20Greenlight%20expects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BTail%20protection%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20dollar%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGreenlight%20has%20added%20this%20position%20in%20the%20case%20the%20greenback%20falls%20substantially%20against%20the%20euro%20and%20yen.%20This%20has%20already%20been%20happening.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-duration%20inflation%20swaps%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20mentioned%20above%2C%20the%20firm%20predicts%20that%20most%20Trump%20administration%20policies%20will%20result%20in%20higher%20long-term%20inflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-einhorn-greenlight-capital-q1-letter-gold-sp500-bear-market-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744922261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68015910c6ad288d147e7d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-einhorn-greenlight-capital-q1-letter-gold-sp500-bear-market-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22David%20Einhorn's%20Greenlight%20Capital%20says%20a%20bear%20market%20in%20stocks%20has%20already%20started%2C%20and%20that%20they're%20making%20a%20handful%20of%20defensive%20trades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40businessinsider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-einhorn-greenlight-capita