certainly%20not%20a%20cheap%20purchase%20for%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20actually%20worth%20spending%20that%20much%20for%20a%20towel%20warmer%3F%20Do%20these%20bathroom%20gadgets%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hype%20on%20social%20media%3F%20We%20wanted%20to%20find%20out%2C%20so%20I%20put%20this%20best-selling%20model%20in%20my%20home%20for%20around%20a%20month%20to%20see%20how%20it%20upgrades%20an%20everyday%20experience%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-towels%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20towels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Spoiler%20alert%3A%20I%20fell%20in%20love!%20Here's%20what%20makes%20this%20towel%20warmer%20so%20great%20and%20why%20you%20should%20definitely%20consider%20adding%20one%20to%20your%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f003b53b-735d-4c45-914c-f6d27c601044%5C%22%3EDesign%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20on%20a%20hardwood%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680015ea3fe8d39283634647%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Zadro%20Large%20Bucket%20Towel%20Warmer%20has%20a%20sleek%2C%20minimalistic%20design%20with%20%26quot%3Bbamboo%26quot%3B%20accents.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20its%20name%20suggests%2C%20the%20Zadro%20Large%20Bucket%20Towel%20Warmer%20is%20essentially%20a%20large%2C%2020-liter%20bucket%20with%20a%20lift-off%20lid.%20It%20comes%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20color%20options%2C%20and%20I%20tested%20the%20white%20bucket%20with%20bamboo%20accents.%20The%20exterior%20of%20the%20unit%20and%20its%20lid%20are%20both%20made%20of%20heavy%20duty%20plastic%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bbamboo%26quot%3B%20accents%20are%20also%20plastic%20%E2%80%94%20I%20expected%20them%20to%20be%20real%20wood%20given%20the%20product's%20price%20point%2C%20and%20up%20close%2C%20they%20look%20a%20bit%20cheap.%20The%20interior%20of%20the%20bucket%20is%20made%20from%20stainless%20steel%20for%20durability%20and%20corrosion-resistance%2C%20and%20there's%20also%20a%20cord%20wrap%20underneath%20the%20bucket%20where%20you%20can%20wind%20up%20the%2083-inch%20power%20cord%2C%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20is%20very%20user-friendly%2C%20with%20just%20two%20buttons%20for%20operation.%20There's%20a%20power%20button%2C%20which%20you%20have%20to%20hold%20down%20for%20three%20seconds%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20towel%20warmer.%20The%20second%20button%20lets%20you%20cycle%20through%20the%20unit's%20timer%20settings.%20You%20can%20set%20the%20bucket%20to%20stay%20on%20for%2015%2C%2030%2C%2045%2C%20or%2060%20minutes%2C%20after%20which%20it%20will%20automatically%20shut%20off.%20For%20safety%20reasons%2C%20there's%20no%20option%20to%20leave%20the%20warmer%20on%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20turn%20the%20towel%20warmer%20on%2C%20its%20LED%20indicator%20light%20turns%20blue%20to%20let%20you%20know%20it's%20preheating.%20When%20it%20reaches%20its%20%26quot%3Boptimal%20heating%20temperature%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20light%20turns%20red%20and%20starts%20the%20timer.%20After%20the%20unit%20is%20powered%20off%2C%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3BHot%20Surface%26quot%3B%20LED%20indicator%20that%20stays%20lit%20until%20the%20interior%20of%20the%20bucket%20is%20cool%20enough%20to%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afd6c5d7-e7b9-41bc-8ce5-3479bc74a3b1%5C%22%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20of%20the%20Zadro%20towel%20warmer%2C%20with%20power%20and%20timer%20buttons.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680016bfa466d2b74ab35f42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20time%20the%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20so%20your%20towel%20is%20fresh%20and%20warm%20when%20you're%20finished%20showering.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20tested%20the%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20in%20our%20bathroom%20for%20several%20weeks.%20Once%20you%20turn%20it%20on%2C%20it%20takes%20just%20three%20minutes%20to%20preheat%2C%20after%20which%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20bucket%20are%20around%20118%20degrees%20(as%20measured%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermometer).%20However%2C%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bucket%20doesn't%20heat%20up%20at%20all%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20only%20heating%20elements%20on%20the%20sides%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can't%20adjust%20the%20temperature%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20little%20trial%20and%20error%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20best%20way%20to%20insert%20towels%20into%20the%20bucket.%20At%20first%2C%20we%20tried%20folding%20or%20rolling%20them%20up%2C%20but%20this%20consistently%20left%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20towel%20cold.%20Instead%2C%20we%20found%20it%20was%20better%20to%20drape%20towels%20in%20loosely%20to%20maximize%20the%20surface%20area%20that%20touches%20the%20sides.%20The%20bucket%20is%20big%20enough%20to%20fit%20two%20full-size%20bath%20towels%2C%20and%20I've%20also%20used%20it%20to%20warm%20up%20my%20bathrobe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20general%20consensus%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20use%20is%20that%20your%20towel%20needs%20%3Cem%3Eat%20least%3C%2Fem%3E%2010%20minutes%20to%20heat%20up%20%E2%80%94%20but%20ideally%2015%20minutes%20or%20more.%20If%20you%20take%20it%20out%20any%20sooner%2C%20there%20are%20cold%20spots%20on%20the%20towel%20which%20can%20ruin%20your%20experience.%20I%20tend%20to%20take%20quick%2010-minute%20showers%2C%20so%20I%20found%20it%20works%20best%20to%20turn%20the%20warmer%20on%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20come%20upstairs%2C%20giving%20it%20ample%20time%20to%20heat%20my%20towel%20up%20evenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%3A%20I%20wasn't%20sure%20whether%20I%20would%20even%20like%20having%20my%20towels%20warmed%2C%20but%20I%20became%20a%20convert%20after%20the%20first%20use.%20Wrapping%20up%20in%20a%20warm%20towel%20on%20a%20chilly%20day%20is%20absolutely%20luxurious%2C%20and%20both%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20now%20use%20the%20device%20daily!%20The%20towels%20are%20always%20cozy%20and%20welcoming%20without%20being%20%3Cem%3Etoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20hot%2C%20and%20I'm%20particularly%20looking%20forward%20to%20using%20the%20warmer%20during%20the%20cold%20New%20England%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20uses%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%20to%20take%20a%20towel's%20temperature.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680017483fe8d392836346b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20a%20infrared%20thermometer%20to%20measure%20how%20hot%20and%20uniform%20the%20towels%20warmed.%20%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20using%20the%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20as%20part%20of%20my%20everyday%20routine%2C%20I%20also%20ran%20a%20few%20structured%20tests%20on%20it%20to%20measure%20its%20heating%20abilities.%20My%20towel%20started%20out%20at%20around%2064%20degrees%20(roughly%20room%20temperature)%2C%20and%20after%2010%20minutes%20in%20the%20bucket%2C%20most%20of%20the%20towel%20measured%20in%20between%20105%20and%20120%20degrees.%20However%2C%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20towel%20that%20was%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bucket%20was%20only%2075%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20these%20measurements%20again%20after%2020%20minutes%2C%20and%20the%20heat%20was%20more%20uniform%20across%20the%20towel.%20Most%20areas%20measured%20between%20110%20and%20130%20degrees%2C%20but%20I%20was%20disappointed%20to%20find%20that%20the%20bottom%20was%20still%20just%2090%20degrees.%20The%20warmth%20of%20the%20towel%20also%20seemed%20to%20max%20out%20at%20this%20point%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20still%20the%20same%20temperature%20after%2030%20minutes%20in%20the%20bucket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d8b47d9-b5f3-45e9-add3-15f8e0aa9baa%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22towel%20inside%20of%20a%20towel%20warmer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680139d4c6ad288d147e7666%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bucket%20can%20fit%20up%202%20towels%20at%20a%20time%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20some%20time%20for%20the%20towel%20to%20evenly%20heat.%20%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20biggest%20complaint%20about%20the%20Zadro%20Large%20Bucket%20Towel%20Warmer%20is%20simply%20that%20it%20takes%20quite%20a%20while%20to%20evenly%20heat%20up%20a%20towel.%20If%20I%20put%20my%20towel%20into%20it%20right%20as%20I'm%20getting%20into%20the%20shower%2C%20it%20typically%20has%20cold%20spots%20that%20ruin%20its%20toasty%20warm%20feel.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20it%20does%20take%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20pre-planning%20for%20optimal%20results%20(unless%20you%20take%20longer%20showers%2C%20in%20which%20case%20you%20might%20be%20fine%20using%20it%20this%20way).%20The%20bottom%20of%20the%20towel%20is%20also%20generally%20a%20bit%20cooler%20than%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bucket%20doesn't%20heat%20up%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20inner%20walls%20of%20the%20bucket%20get%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20around%20120%20degrees%20%E2%80%94%20and%20can%20burn%20you.%20You'll%20want%20to%20be%20careful%20inserting%20and%20removing%20your%20towels%2C%20and%20you%20should%20keep%20children%20away%20from%20the%20bucket%20while%20it's%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222275de1-eaa0-4476-ae98-e0df03817da5%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22zadro%20towel%20warmer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680139d43fe8d39283636052%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20new%20favorite%20shower%20upgrade.%3Cp%3ECamryn%20Rabideau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20testing%2C%20I%20was%20a%20little%20skeptical%20of%20whether%20I%20really%20%3Cem%3Eneeded%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20towel%20warmer%2C%20but%20after%20a%20month%20of%20use%2C%20I%20can%20officially%20say%20I'm%20a%20convert.%20It's%20such%20a%20luxury%20to%20have%20a%20cozy%20warm%20towel%20waiting%20when%20you%20step%20out%20of%20the%20shower%2C%20especially%20on%20cold%20days%2C%20and%20the%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20is%20really%20simple%20to%20use.%20The%20bucket%20is%20big%20enough%20to%20hold%20two%20towels%20at%20a%20time%2C%20and%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20find%20a%20space%20for%20the%20bucket-style%20warmer%20in%20our%20bathroom%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20small%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Zadro%20Towel%20Warmer%20is%20a%20bit%20expensive%2C%20retailing%20for%20around%20%24170%20at%20full%20price%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20buy%20if%20you%20want%20to%20elevate%20your%20self-care%20routine.%20It%20would%20also%20make%20a%20wonderful%20housewarming%20or%20wedding%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fzadro-towel-warmer-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744916402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680017f3c6ad288d147e5cea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fzadro-towel-warmer-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tried%20the%20Zadro%20Large%20Bucket%20Towel%20Warmer.%20It%20warms%20up%20to%20two%20towels%20at%20a%20time%20for%20a%20cozy%20post-shower%20experience%20and%20easy%20bathroom%20upgrade.%22%2C%